{"submitted": "2025-10-15T11:14:35.082-05:00", "type": "g2_incentivized", "region": "Asia", "updated": "2025-10-15T11:14:35.132-05:00", "url": "https://www.g2.com/products/sap-cloud-erp-sap-s-4hana-cloud/reviews/11814541", "title": "Learning Curve", "primary": "Asia Pacific", "switched_from": {"products": [{"id": "428", "name": "Dynamics 365 Sales", "slug": "dynamics-365-sales"}], "reason": "We switched to SAP S/4HANA Cloud because our previous on-premise ERP system lacked real-time data visibility, scalability, and automation. It required a lot of manual effort for reporting, reconciliation, and financial closing, which slowed down decision-making and increased the risk of errors.

In comparison, SAP S/4HANA Cloud offers a modern, integrated, and intelligent platform that connects all our key business functions — finance, procurement, and analytics — in one place. The real-time insights, faster processing speeds, and automated workflows have made a huge difference in productivity and accuracy.

Unlike our old system, which required heavy maintenance and upgrades, the cloud model keeps everything up-to-date automatically, saving time and operational costs. Overall, SAP S/4HANA Cloud is more efficient, agile, and future-ready, giving us the flexibility our business needed."}}

